				<title>Accessibility Audit for Aljazeera English Website</title>
				        
				
					<description>&lt;p&gt;While checking my Twitter feed, I noticed a tweet of a medium &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/@ajlabs/a-look-into-how-and-why-aljazeera-com-embarked-on-a-redesign-d50525ceb09c#.xuc54w2q7&quot;&gt;article&lt;/a&gt; on the redesign of &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.aljazeera.com&quot;&gt;Aljazeera.com&lt;/a&gt;. As a curious designer, I read the whole article and loved the new design. But, in terms accessibility, there are a lot of missing things in the website. I will point out all issues that make browsing hard for keyboard and screen reader users.&lt;/p&gt;

